ns  The staff provides design and production for newsletters  posters  advertisements  etc  Go to Publications   Media Relations For information about events and issues  faculty expertise  fact sheets and official comments concerning the Institute  please visit Media Relations  Go to Media Relations   MarketingCommunications and Marketing is responsible for building brand loyalty  brand awareness  enhancing efforts of the Institute to build a dynamic Corps of citizen soldiers and communicating the character strength of a VMI graduate  Go to Marketing   Web ServicesFor assistance with updating current departmental websites  developing new sites or other issues related to the Institute website contact us  Go to Web Services   Institute Report Cadet Handbook Academic Catalog Identity Standards VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 